Package rs.fon.whibo.GDT.treeModel

Provides classes that algorithms use to build a tree model.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GDTTestUtil  
    NominalSplitCondition
    A split condition for nominal values (equals).
    WhiboAbstractSplitCondition
    The Abstract Split Condition that is used by the TreeModel to define the splits within the tree.
    WhiboGreaterSplitCondition
    Implements the Greater than condition used by the TreeModel.
    WhiboLessEqualsSplitCondition
    Implements the Less or Equals than condition used by the TreeModel.
